---
// Brand page title block — the spec sheet's masthead.
---

<section class="brand-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow brand-hero__kicker" data-reveal>Brand Guidelines &mdash; The Measured Index</p>
    <h1 class="t-hero brand-hero__title" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 120ms">
      One system, <em>measured</em>.
    </h1>
    <p class="t-body brand-hero__lede" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 260ms">
      A warm-ivory editorial broadsheet where type does almost everything and restraint is
      the device. Two families, one accent, hairline rules. Everything on this page is driven
      by the same design tokens the site ships &mdash; change a token, change the brand.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .brand-hero {
    padding-block: clamp(3.5rem, 9vh, 7rem) clamp(2.5rem, 6vh, 4.5rem);
  }
  .brand-hero__kicker {
    margin-bottom: clamp(1.5rem, 4vh, 2.5rem);
  }
  .brand-hero__title {
    max-width: 18ch;
  }
  .brand-hero__lede {
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin-top: clamp(1.5rem, 4vh, 2.5rem);
    color: var(--text);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
</style>
